{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>Spready</i>, solve unique 3D puzzles with optical illusions to guide artists through their challenges and conflicts as they bring artworks to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The essence of artists' lives and journeys lies within the paintings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To create a perfect piece, you must utilize various gimmicks to color every inch of the canvas without leaving any gaps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Crayon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/\uc2a4\ud300\uc6c0\uc9e41.gif?t=1729521813\" />Move the crayons placed on the canvas. You can color the canvas! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Bent canvas &amp; Eraser</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/\uc2a4\ud300\uc6c0\uc9e42.gif?t=1729521813\" />Abandon the bias that the canvas is flat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even a bent canvas can be colored as much as you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And try using an eraser on the parts you want to erase!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wheel</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/\uc2a4\ud300\uc6c0\uc9e43.gif?t=1729521813\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have a bent canvas, there's also a rotating canvas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use wheels to freely rotate the canvas while coloring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Duplicate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/\uc2a4\ud300\uc6c0\uc9e44.gif?t=1729521813\" />What will happen when you overlap canvases behind other canvases?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try duplicating crayons ans erasers to fill in any missing parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Optical illusion Connection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944240/extras/\uc2a4\ud300\uc6c0\uc9e45.gif?t=1729521813\" />Use optical illusions to move the crayon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll be able to color canvases that are far away.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beautiful Wave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/2167ff6eddc90af7c4e76abf8376516d23feda83.jpg"},{"name":"Wings of Freedom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/46a43a61f5bc242023c20bd2ea3ccf5b7982ff53.jpg"},{"name":"Against Destiny","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/917fe6a34e03b88feebe0077a15af1d3804a28b9.jpg"},{"name":"With Conviction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/96d199b153637a266f29174d3df1e16bd2792a0e.jpg"},{"name":"Back to Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/14da299ff1721d3e83e6b96a5e732c362f746d9f.jpg"},{"name":"Worker's Art","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/29ab4c6e680e39ead7af62ff28d019e59e8e88a1.jpg"},{"name":"To a Wider World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/c74a590a56890d27e64283d973940d91121d12f6.jpg"},{"name":"Tough Choice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944240/6a804afbd27165bb9d7be